866
01:29:06,842 --> 01:29:10,301
The city of Jezreel.

867
01:29:10,387 --> 01:29:12,344
Town of Megiddo.

868
01:29:13,682 --> 01:29:16,049
The place...

869
01:29:16,142 --> 01:29:18,474
